value.snippet: KIC is a technology company working to make reflow ovens smarter through thermal profiling, automation and optimization solutions. With offices across the globe, KIC is ready to become your partner in oven based manufacturing.

value.name: Kirsten Christiansen, Advokatsekretær
value.snippet: Kirsten Christiansen er advokatsekretær i Offentlig Ret. Hun løser i samarbejde med advokater og fuldmægtige opgaver i forbindelse med forberedelse af retssager mv. Står desuden for kvalitetssikring, korrektur og overholdelse af de deadlines, som er forbundet hermed.

value.name: Reflow Ovens Thermal Profiling
value.snippet: KIC offers you temperature data logging tools for setting up your oven or wave solder machine. This includes: Flexibility State-of-the-art hardware technology and capability Simplified setup and operation Basic data collection and reporting See How it Works Automated Process Optimization You’re in control.

value.name: Početna - Kulturno Informativni Centar Podgorica
value.snippet: Dobro došli u Javnu ustanovu Kulturno – informativni centar „Budo Tomović“ (KIC) čiji je osnivač Glavni grad Podgorica. U svom poluvjekovnom trajanju, KIC je postao centar kreativnog stvaranja, jedno od najznačajnijih središta crnogorske kulture, a na scenama KIC-a stasale su brojne generacije stvaralaca u svim domenima.
